# Middleware templates (from `middleware.json`)

The list currently contains **1** file under **`**/middleware/**`**: `app/middleware/requestContext.ts` (see [`.agents/file-lists/middleware.json`](../file-lists/middleware.json)).

## Pattern — React Router middleware + context

```typescript
import type { RouterContextProvider } from "react-router";
import { createContext, type MiddlewareFunction } from "react-router";

export interface RequestContext {
  readonly id: string;
  readonly ip: string | null;
}

const requestContext = createContext<RequestContext>();

export const requestContextMiddleware: MiddlewareFunction<Response> = async ({ request, context }, next) => {
  context.set(requestContext, {
    id: `${Date.now()}${Math.random()}`,
    ip: null,
  });

  return next();
};

export function getRequestContext(context: Readonly<RouterContextProvider>): RequestContext {
  return context.get(requestContext);
}
```

## Notes

- Keep **context types** small and **readonly**.
- Prefer **pure** helpers for reading context; side effects stay in the middleware body.

